    "name": "Kamaitachie",
    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Kamaitachis revel in causing pain. A kamaitachi might, for example, hold someone hostage with its delayed doom ability and force that person (or one of the victim\u2019s loved ones) to commit horrible or demeaning acts in exchange for the hostage\u2019s life. Of course, depending on its fickle mood, the kamaitachi is just as likely to kill a hostage who meets its demands."
        }
    ],
